- produced: cover-letter.md (800 words, Michael's voice, no banned phrasing), one-pager.html (22KB, industrial design, screenshots embedded, all 8 requirements), deck.pptx (8 slides, 1.9MB, screenshots embedded, dark industrial theme)
- decisions: design matches demo palette (#F76B10 / #1C1F24), not portfolio palette; screenshots referenced as relative paths from same directory; mocked payment flagged explicitly in all three; github.com/mwegter95 used throughout
- next needs: evaluator can verify all 8 requirements addressed in cover letter AND demo; check no em/en dashes; verify demo link and github handle
- risks: one-pager screenshot paths are relative (work in browser opened from the run directory; may need adjustments if served from a different path)
